sections.title: Contact
sections.content: Do you have any questions? Or would you like to schedule a consultation? Send us a message and we will get back to you shortly.

sections.title: Web Services
sections.content: We are a Vancouver based company focusing on creating high quality responsive websites for small to medium sized businesses at an affordable price.

sections.title: Features
sections.subtitle: We know that creating or expanding an online presence can be time consuming and overwhelming. Here we have broken down a few key features we use to help make your life easier.

features.title: Responsive Websites
features.image_alt: App preview on a phone and tablet
features.content: The tools we use to create your site have been designed on a responsive platform that focuses on a mobile first approach. Which means your users will get a great experience wether they are on a mobile device or desktop computer.

features.title: Fast and Secure
features.image_alt: App users welcoming a new member
features.content: Nobody wants to wait for a slow site to load. We use the latest software and plugins available when building your site as well as making sure your site has an SSL certificate.

features.title: Working Together
features.content: We will make sure that your needs are met every step of the way. Once complete we will take the time to make sure that you are completely satisfied with the end product.
